{"tid":727628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世足賽》輸球後還清理休息室 日本隊讓FIFA大讚","createTime":"2018-07-03T07:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T08:12:08.000Z","uid":49391,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"46b3327096d57231d58c81b8836cf87888e66d56","tid":727628,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2018/07/03/phpZRlitW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2FphpZRlitW.jpg&h=b58f0ebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本隊輸球。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔記者倪婉君／綜合報導〕「這是日本隊在第94分鐘輸給比利時之後，休息室的模樣。」國際足總（FIFA）營運主管詹森絲（Priscilla Janssens）在推特上貼出一張日本隊休息室在賽後打掃得一塵不染的照片，她直呼真是「所有球隊的榜樣」!<br />\n<br />\n日本隊今以2：3不敵比利時，賽後不少球員淚灑球場的模樣讓球迷不捨，但他們仍打起精神向場邊的球迷鞠躬致謝。回到休息室後，一張由FIFA人員曝光的照片，更讓外界對日本隊的風度佩服不已。<br />\n<br />\n在詹森絲的照片中，日本隊不但將休息室打掃得乾乾淨淨，而且還在櫃子上擺了一張用俄文寫的「謝謝」，向工作人員致意，也讓詹森絲寫下日本隊是所有球隊的榜樣，能和日本隊共事更是莫大榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n日本球迷這次在離場之前會主動清理垃圾的行為，已獲外媒大讚為「最棒的客人」，如今日本隊在輸球後仍然展現風度清理休息室的舉動，更是獲得好評。<br />\n<br />\nThis is the Japanese dressingroom after losing to Belgium in the 94&rsquo; minute. Thanked their fans in the stadium, cleaned up everything （bench and dressingroom） and spoke to media. Even left note with &lsquo;thank you&rsquo; in Russian. What an example for all teams!! Privilege to work with! <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/eIryTdrlKA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FeIryTdrlKA&d=Q9EuaZy05Qwl7heWc3LCFwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=6cd01a2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/eIryTdrlKA</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; Priscilla Janssens （priscillaboca） 2018年7月2日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2018/07/03/phpnHP4fK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2FphpnHP4fK.jpg&h=53d8162a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本球迷賽後收拾垃圾。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2018/07/03/phpeKufPu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2FphpeKufPu.jpg&h=44c9f68e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本球迷賽後收拾垃圾。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2018/07/03/phpg1d6S1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2Fphpg1d6S1.jpg&h=a8de47c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本隊惜敗，球迷失望。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2018/07/03/phpBsRtUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2FphpBsRtUj.jpg&h=fb115690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本隊惜敗，球迷失望。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2476349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2476349&d=Q9EuaZy05Qwl7heWc3LCFwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=8d7e138a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2476349&h=aed32263\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2476349</a>"},{"pid":"379cdc8246e9b43ed694d5b05b1be31665064efa","tid":727628,"uid":57835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"尾二張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed4520d269c5b39a406f665925f451f5e04282a","tid":727628,"uid":49391,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:22:00.000Z","msg":"港豬:唔好執走D垃圾呀,無曬垃圾D清潔呀姐咪失業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b7068d5b74ecd5ed9472d0fed0afd274853318","tid":727628,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"379cdc8246e9b43ed694d5b05b1be31665064efa","tid":727628,"uid":57835,"like":4,"dislike":